FTPGINDD.text:
//INPUT    DD *
SITE NOISPFSTATS
BINARY
STRUCTURE RECORD

FTPGNVSM.text:
DEFINE NONVSAM( -
            NAME(&NDSN) -
            DEVICETYPES(3390) -
            VOLUMES(&PLXVOL) ) -
           CATALOG(&CATALOG)

FTPGPRM1.text:
site lrecl=&LRECL blksize=&BLK recfm=&RF pdstype=&PDST
site &SU pri=&PRI sec=&SEC dir=&DIR vol=&PLXVOL
site cond=delete mg=software retpd
cd '&PNDSN'
mkd '&NDSN'
cd '&NDSN'
lcd '&DSN'
mput *

FTPGPRM2.text:
site lrecl=&LRECL blksize=&BLK recfm=&RF pdstype=&PDST
site &SU pri=&PRI sec=&SEC vol=&PLXVOL
site cond=delete mg=software retpd
cd '&PNDSN'
mkd '&NDSN'
cd '&NDSN'
lcd '&DSN'
mput *

FTPGPRM3.text:
site lrecl=&LRECL blksize=&BLK recfm=&RF
site &SU pri=&PRI sec=&SEC vol=&PLXVOL
site cond=delete mg=software retpd
put '&DSN' +
    '&NDSN'
